  exerciseText: Not dealing damage
  hintText: Log the HealthBar .fillAmount
  solutionText: 'Wrong math on GetHealthBarNormalized();

    The correct way is
    to divide the current amount by the max, not the other way around

    return
    (float)healthAmount / healthAmountMax;'
